                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9686" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2419</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1130 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">弃旧扬新，酿就香醇：雀巢的数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Abandoning the Old and Promoting the New to Brew Rich Aroma The Digital Transformation Path of Nestl&#233;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱强，梅欣然，余悦，陈安澜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雀巢中国有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；雀巢公司；供应链数字化；资源编排；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Transformation; Nestl&#233;; Supply Chain Digitization; Resource Orchestration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球经济与信息技术迅猛发展下，快消品行业面临渠道与顾客相关的诸多挑战。消费群体变化，年轻群体追个性差异，中产阶级重高质安全，需求趋于多样，传统经销模式虽有成本与回款优势，但远离消费者致市场敏感度缺失，且行业多未重视数字化转型。雀巢却积极推进数字化转型战略，实现业务创新突破。本案例以雀巢为研究对象，从行业背景出发，先剖析其数字化转型内外部动因，探究国内传统供应链管理弊端与数字化雏形。再依其转型路径，阐述从供应链数字化到 “以消费者为核心” 平台构建，再到中台建设的全链路数字化详情。最后总结雀巢转型经验，得出可供快消品行业借鉴的数字化转型建议，助力其他企业实践。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the rapid development of the global economy and IT, the FMCG industry faces many challenges related to channels and customers. Consumer groups are changing, with the young seeking individuality and the middle class valuing high quality and safety, making demands more diverse. The traditional distribution model has cost and payment advantages but lacks market sensitivity due to being far from consumers, and many industries haven&#39;t emphasized digital transformation. However, Nestle actively promotes its digital transformation strategy and achieves business innovation breakthroughs. This case study takes Nestle as the research object. Starting from the industry background, it first analyzes the internal and external drivers of its digital transformation, explores the drawbacks of traditional supply chain management and the digital prototype in China. Then, based on its transformation path, it elaborates on the full-link digitalization from supply chain digitalization to the construction of a &quot;consumer-centered&quot; platform and then to the middle platform. Finally, it summarizes Nestle&#39;s transformation experience and obtains digital transformation suggestions for the FMCG industry to assist other enterprises in practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；资源编排</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
